                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1492798679147-confidentiality--rights-and-obligations-of-ryerson-university-committee-members" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1492798679147-confidentiality--rights-and-obligations-of-ryerson-university-committee-members">
